						<div class="postbody">The PowerPak does offer a lot of hardware power to homebrewers but remember if someone wants to publish their game, fancy stuff doesn't fit into discrete logic or even CPLD. So at least in my case, there's little motivation to stray from conventional hardware options.</div>

